<emphasis id="29BD9F1E08717739FF05FF42FEFFFF7E" bold="true" box="[151,331,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Cladonia grayi</emphasis>
G. Merr. ex Sandst. (1929: 1847)
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
